title: 835. Bruce Feldman on USC, UCLA Leaving the Pac-12 & the College Football Landscape
itunes:title: 835. Bruce Feldman on USC, UCLA Leaving the Pac-12 & the College Football Landscape
description:
Bucky Brooks is back with a new episode of Move the Sticks and is joined by college football reporter and insider Bruce Feldman throughout the show. The guys discuss the impact of USC and UCLA moving from the Pac-12 to the Big Ten in 2024, what the future holds for the Pac-12, what's happening with Notre Dame down the line, college quarterbacks to watch out for, and much more.


Move the Sticks is a part of the NFL Podcasts Network.
